      "date": "2013-12-06 15:57:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/db2c45f6-5e87-11e3-8901-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  3 tests failed: sanity-hsm, lustre-rsync-test, sanityn.",
